         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 118, recto: (1) Harsiesis, son o f Pamonthes, says to (2) Phthoumonthes, son of Phthoumonthes, son of Hor----, (3) I am paid 4 staters / 2 staters / [4 staters again], (4) for the silver of poll of year 43 in Jeme. (5) Written in year 43 of Caesar, (6) 4th month ....</ab>
